summary: "Gallifrey!" The Doctor vs Empress of the Racnoss | The Runaway Bride | ...  Rewatching this scene from Doctor Who, I'm reminded...
caption:
“Gallifrey!” The Doctor vs Empress of the Racnoss | The Runaway Bride | …

Rewatching this scene from Doctor Who, I’m reminded of the very moment I fell in love with Donna Noble as a character.
She’s funny, witty, stubborn, and good-hearted–all powerful assets of any companion to the Doctor, but when she said: “Doctor, you can stop now!” and the Doctor actually listened, I knew she was a character I can completely, unconditionally get behind.

Support comes in many ways. Some ways are “GO!”, other (more easily misinterpreted) ways are “NO!”

#BringBackDoctorDonna
